data.description: Complete move in ready 3 BR 2 bath home with a non-conforming 4th bedroom in basement located in the beautiful City of Cumberland and within walking distance to boat landing on Beaver Dam Lake.  Charm and character are located throughout this home including arched doorways and coved ceilings.  This home boasts freshly painted rooms; new flooring, remodeled main floor bath and refreshed kitchen leading you to a great lower level family room space and additional bathroom.  Fantastic storage space throughout the home.  The backyard screened in porch leads to a newly fenced in back yard with relaxing firepit area.
